        "A. Management review must be conducted at planned intervals, considering audit results, non-conformities, and changes in internal/external context"
      ],
      "correct": 3,
      "justification_correct": "Clause 9.3 mandates management review at planned intervals, evaluating ISMS suitability, adequacy, effectiveness considering audit results, non-conformities, and internal/external changes, ensuring top-level governance and strategic alignment.",
      "justification_wrong": "Option B contradicts 9.3.1 requirement for planned reviews; C excludes ISMS performance from scope; D specifies unrealistic daily frequency incompatible with 'planned intervals' concept in normative requirements."
