    {
      "num": 14,
      "text": "In ISO 27001:2022 clause 9.1, what is required regarding the monitoring and measurement of information security processes?",
      "tag": "Monitoring and Measurement",
      "options": [
        "B. Monitoring is required only when information security incidents occur",
        "C. Measurement activities are exclusively the responsibility of external consultants and auditors",
