        "A. Organizations must determine what needs monitoring, methods for monitoring, and establish performance criteria, with results analyzed and reported"
      ],
      "correct": 3,
      "justification_correct": "Clause 9.1 requires determining monitoring needs, methods, analysis of results, and performance evaluation criteria. This systematic approach ensures ISMS effectiveness verification and data-driven decision making for continuous improvement.",
