    },
    {
      "num": 15,
      "text": "According to ISO 27001:2022 clause 10.2, how must the organization approach continual improvement of the ISMS?",
      "tag": "Continual Improvement",
      "options": [
        "A. The organization must improve the ISMS on an ongoing basis using results from monitoring, measurement, analysis, management review, and corrective actions",
