      "correct": 0,
      "justification_correct": "Clause 10.2 establishes continual improvement as an ongoing process using audit results, monitoring data, non-conformity management, and management review outcomes. This integrated approach ensures systematic, evidence-based ISMS enhancement aligned with organizational objectives.",
      "justification_wrong": "Option B treats improvement as reactive; C conflates improvement with technology adoption unrelated to ISMS objectives; D unnecessarily separates improvement from integrated governance, contradicting holistic ISMS approach required by the standard."
